Description:

  zstatus is a swaybar status command in Zig.

  It is tailored to my specific needs.

  It updates the time every second and the temperature every 30 minutes.

  Branch main is compatible with zig 0.14.1

  Branch zig-0.16.0-dev is compatible with zig 0.16.0-dev.1412

Usage:

  $ zig build

  Edit .config/sway/config

    status_command /path/to/zstatus <latitude> <longitude>

    Example:

    status_command /path/to/zstatus 47.374 8.531

